column5: Well went out for trout opener to st.johns CA for some rainbows went with my Buddy Terrance (TC10Z) and when we got there the pond didnt open for fishing till noon luckily it was 1130 so we just spent time rigging up and getting bait on, 5 mins after first cast my float is gone and I cant seem to see it anywere than I reeled in and set the hook and Wham a nice 11.5" rainbow well several grueling hours later and a few miss strikes we move to this other spot and land on a school and we than Limit out what a day had one on that jumped a good 2 feet in air got it close to shore and it shook loose little bugger.  now for some fish PORN!!!!!!
thats a cute trout lol gj
Was a great day. First time ever targeting this species. Not really my thing but at least I can say I've gotten one.
Good one guys, good start Terrance....very good practice run for the big one to get team 5 back in the running
